! CAUTION !

This software is for my own use.
You can use this software only if you read all of source codes and
you should recognize what it is.


INSTALLATION

1. git clone https://github.com/hiratara/lambdabot-hipchat-plugins.git
2. Build lambdabot-hipchat-plugins
3. git clone https://github.com/mokus0/lambdabot.git
4. Modify lambdabot/lambdabot.cabal and lambdabot/src/Modules.hs
   to integrate lambdabot-hipchat-plugin into lambdabot.
5. Build lambdabot and run it
